<i>adjective</i>: 더덕더덕하다 [더덕떠더카다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>더덕더덕하다 [더덕떠더카다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. clustered</dd><br>
<dd>조그마한 것들이 한곳에 많이 지저분하게 붙어 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being in a state in which a large number of small things are attached to something in a messy concentration.</dd><br>
<dd>2. full of patches</dd><br>
<dd>보기 흉할 만큼 지저분하게 여기저기 기워 놓은 데가 많다.</dd><br>
<dd>Having so many patches sewn on something as to make it look shabby.</dd><br>
<dd>3. bedaubed</dd><br>
<dd>화장을 아주 짙게 한 상태이다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being in the state of putting on a thick layer of makeup.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>